---
title: Cheesy Melt in the Middle Beef Burger with Wedges and Balsamic Baby Leaf Salad
description: This Cheesy Melt in the Middle Beef Burger is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
